### Email 2 — Summer Internship Interest

| Field | Detail |
|---|---|
| **From** | Student (Aarav Mehta) |
| **To** | Internship Coordinator at Technovance Technologies |
| **Subject** | Application for Summer Internship Opportunity – Computer Science Student (May–July 2026) |
| **Purpose** | Expressing genuine interest in an internship, highlighting relevant skills and attaching documents |
| **File** | `professional-emails.md` |

### Email Etiquette Rules Applied

- ✅ Clear, specific subject line
- ✅ Professional salutation (Dear [Name/Title])
- ✅ Structured body: purpose → context → request/action → closing
- ✅ Polite and formal tone throughout
- ✅ Proper sign-off with full name and contact details
- ✅ No slang, abbreviations, or informal language

