## Part B – Social Media Do's and Don'ts Checklist

A checklist with **7 Do's and 7 Don'ts** (exceeding the minimum of 5 each) has been created for responsible social media use as a college student.

📄 **File:** `social-media-checklist.md`

### Highlights from the Checklist

| ✅ Do | ❌ Don't |
|---|---|
| Think before you post | Post offensive or hateful content |
| Use privacy settings | Share personal details publicly |
| Credit original creators | Engage in or ignore cyberbullying |
| Verify before sharing | Accept requests from unknown strangers |
| Maintain professional profiles | Vent publicly about institutions or people |

